      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/maine-voters-platner.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[许多选民表示，他们预计该州民主党参议员候选人格雷厄姆·普拉特纳(Graham Platner)在前女友公开指控他性侵犯后退出竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/maine-voters-platner.html</guid>
